Class ActivationLayer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.lang.ReferenceCountingBase

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MultiPrecision<ActivationLayer>, Layer, ReferenceCounting, Serializable

    public class ActivationLayer
extends LayerBase
implements MultiPrecision<ActivationLayer>
    The generic Activation key, exposing the activation types provided by CudaSystem. This key is stateless and is determined by a univariate function, e.g. ReLU or Sigmoid.
